WEBVTT

01:37.950 --> 01:40.520
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.350 --> 01:43.690
[Episode 19]

02:00.640 --> 02:02.170
Immortal, please remember

02:02.710 --> 02:05.000
to keep composed, calm,

02:05.200 --> 02:06.930
and concentrated all the time.

02:07.150 --> 02:09.000
If you can't find the gate,

02:09.280 --> 02:11.630
by no means should you force yourself.

02:34.000 --> 02:34.600
Immortal,

02:35.470 --> 02:37.000
have you found that person?

02:41.310 --> 02:42.910
If not, just give up.

02:43.760 --> 02:46.360
You've been in your spiritual sea
for a long time.

02:46.360 --> 02:47.340
At this rate,

02:47.680 --> 02:49.610
your divine sense will be damaged,

02:49.630 --> 02:50.310
Immortal.

03:40.280 --> 03:41.340
Get the basin here.

03:52.960 --> 03:53.820
Let me feed him.

03:55.620 --> 03:56.490
He will wake up

03:56.520 --> 03:57.579
in another 4 hours.

03:57.910 --> 03:58.870
If he experiences

03:58.870 --> 04:00.190
any weakness in the limbs,

04:00.190 --> 04:01.450
dizziness, or nausea,

04:01.470 --> 04:02.600
consider it normal.

04:02.680 --> 04:04.310
Feed him medicine every 4 hours.

04:04.310 --> 04:06.000
Then he will recover in 3 to 5 days.

04:06.000 --> 04:07.030
Three to five days?

04:07.030 --> 04:08.190
Does it have to be that long?

04:08.190 --> 04:10.120
A black sandstorm is happening outside.

04:10.120 --> 04:10.630
I'd say it'll last

04:10.630 --> 04:12.280
at least another day and night.

04:12.280 --> 04:13.190
It's hard to determine exactly

04:13.190 --> 04:14.390
how long it will last.

04:14.400 --> 04:15.590
We can't go out anyway.

04:15.590 --> 04:17.320
Might as well stay here for now.

04:18.430 --> 04:18.950
Well...

04:19.730 --> 04:20.130
I...

04:20.160 --> 04:21.240
Who really are you?

04:29.680 --> 04:30.560
My employers.

04:30.920 --> 04:32.380
Didn't I tell you already?

04:32.830 --> 04:34.310
Those immortal sect cultivators are

04:34.310 --> 04:35.710
here to catch you, right?

05:05.040 --> 05:05.800
I... well...

05:06.120 --> 05:06.830
We don't know

05:06.830 --> 05:08.560
any immortal sect cultivators

05:08.600 --> 05:10.260
or what you're talking about.

05:11.040 --> 05:12.500
Penniless though you are,

05:12.600 --> 05:14.630
you hired Lord of Rust-Sword to escort you
along the way.

05:14.630 --> 05:15.890
What are you afraid of?

05:20.160 --> 05:21.680
Given Lord of Rust-Sword's personality,

05:21.680 --> 05:23.270
he would definitely tell you

05:23.270 --> 05:24.000
that he ranks

05:24.310 --> 05:26.640
second on the List of Top Martial Artists.

05:26.920 --> 05:28.630
When the mounted bandits appeared earlier,

05:28.630 --> 05:29.870
you fled in panic

05:29.950 --> 05:31.310
even before seeing them.

05:31.310 --> 05:33.310
Then the young sect master
of Lingji Mountain showed up.

05:33.310 --> 05:35.260
As you learned
he was chasing after a group

05:35.260 --> 05:37.750
of demonic cultivators
who had stolen books,

05:37.750 --> 05:39.080
why did you panic again?

05:39.330 --> 05:40.480
I... I...

05:43.040 --> 05:43.800
What should we do?

05:43.800 --> 05:44.480
What...

05:45.480 --> 05:47.140
are you people talking about?

05:53.630 --> 05:54.270
Immortal.

05:55.070 --> 05:55.670
Immortal!

05:56.070 --> 05:57.270
It's time you woke up!

05:57.750 --> 05:58.350
Immortal.

05:59.120 --> 05:59.830
Immortal?

06:04.390 --> 06:05.250
It's a success.

06:07.310 --> 06:08.110
She found him.

06:15.360 --> 06:16.000
Mr. Lu.

06:18.000 --> 06:18.680
Mr. Lu?

06:18.750 --> 06:19.280
Who is it?

06:20.560 --> 06:21.420
Who's in there?

06:22.510 --> 06:24.040
It's me, Xin Mei.

06:24.240 --> 06:25.040
Where are you?

06:26.310 --> 06:27.570
Who are you talking to?

06:28.120 --> 06:29.580
I'm in your spiritual sea.

06:30.120 --> 06:30.720
Mr. Lu,

06:31.160 --> 06:32.290
please come meet me.

06:43.480 --> 06:45.530
[Lu Qianqiao's spiritual sea]

06:52.750 --> 06:54.750
What brings you to my spiritual sea?

06:54.950 --> 06:57.040
I used the Spirit Projection Technique.

06:57.040 --> 06:58.040
I traveled my spiritual sea

06:58.040 --> 06:59.680
and found the gate leading to you.

06:59.680 --> 07:01.210
That was how I reached here.

07:01.240 --> 07:03.170
The Spirit Projection Technique?

07:03.310 --> 07:04.440
There are thousands

07:04.830 --> 07:06.560
of marks in your spiritual sea.

07:07.040 --> 07:08.720
It's extremely difficult to locate

07:08.720 --> 07:09.800
the gate leading to me.

07:09.800 --> 07:10.860
How did you find it?

07:12.390 --> 07:13.520
I'm not sure myself.

07:14.160 --> 07:15.890
I just thought I'd give it a try.

07:16.000 --> 07:18.190
At first, it was hard to identify
the right gate.

07:18.190 --> 07:18.920
Nonetheless, a blood thread

07:18.920 --> 07:20.070
in me came to my aid.

07:20.830 --> 07:22.230
Following its guidance,

07:22.750 --> 07:23.880
I finally found you.

07:27.000 --> 07:27.750
You're a hybrid of War Demons

07:27.750 --> 07:28.830
and the Human Race,

07:29.120 --> 07:30.680
burdened with the Five Deficiencies Curse.

07:30.680 --> 07:32.600
To get rid of the divine punishment
and reincarnate as a human,

07:32.600 --> 07:33.860
you must pass 5 trials:

07:33.950 --> 07:36.630
skin and flesh replacing, bone renewal,
blood purification, and heart alteration.

07:36.630 --> 07:38.630
Each trial hangs by a thread
between life and death.

07:38.630 --> 07:40.270
You must find a blood relative

07:40.270 --> 07:41.510
to form a blood pact with you

07:41.510 --> 07:43.360
and build a connection
in your spiritual sea,

07:43.360 --> 07:44.920
so when you stand at death's door,

07:44.920 --> 07:46.270
that bond may grant you a lifeline—

07:46.270 --> 07:47.600
a chance to cheat death.

07:48.120 --> 07:49.120
You have no family,

07:49.120 --> 07:50.650
so you have to marry someone

07:50.800 --> 07:52.680
to establish this blood pact.

07:54.630 --> 07:55.890
Why did you come see me?

07:56.159 --> 07:56.920
Don't you know

07:56.920 --> 07:57.920
why I came see you,

08:00.420 --> 08:02.180
Lord Lu Huai?

08:15.950 --> 08:16.390
Miss,

08:16.720 --> 08:18.780
here are the two cloaks you asked for.

08:23.680 --> 08:24.510
What do you think?

08:24.510 --> 08:25.000
Not bad.

08:25.210 --> 08:26.160
Pack them up for me.

08:26.160 --> 08:26.680
Sure.

08:29.920 --> 08:30.520
Thank you.

08:30.920 --> 08:31.980
Sir, do you know any

08:32.000 --> 08:32.750
camel caravan

08:32.750 --> 08:34.320
that is leaving the city soon?

08:34.320 --> 08:35.960
Don't you see
a black sandstorm is approaching?

08:35.960 --> 08:37.360
The wind is already picking up.

08:37.360 --> 08:38.870
No camel caravan
will risk leaving the city.

08:38.870 --> 08:40.200
They are all resting now.

08:40.200 --> 08:41.120
How many days

08:41.120 --> 08:42.520
will the sandstorm last?

08:42.870 --> 08:43.730
Who would know?

08:44.000 --> 08:45.200
When it ends, it ends.

08:48.660 --> 08:50.700
[Tailor Shop]

08:50.440 --> 08:51.370
Take care, miss.

09:31.840 --> 09:33.770
That's the full account of events.

09:34.000 --> 09:34.860
I didn't expect

09:35.320 --> 09:36.320
to meet you again

09:36.320 --> 09:37.520
in Chongling Valley.

09:37.750 --> 09:38.480
So by the time

09:38.480 --> 09:40.140
I woke up at the Safe Haven Inn,

09:40.320 --> 09:41.980
I hadn't had a severe illness.

09:42.240 --> 09:44.040
You had just erased my memories,

09:44.240 --> 09:44.750
right?

09:47.750 --> 09:48.200
Right.

09:48.750 --> 09:49.880
I don't understand.

09:50.630 --> 09:52.230
You have great powers.

09:52.600 --> 09:53.800
In Chongling Valley,

09:53.910 --> 09:55.200
even Cang Fengzi from Tianyuan Sect

09:55.200 --> 09:56.330
was no match for you.

09:57.030 --> 09:57.550
But back then,

09:57.550 --> 09:59.150
why did you let yourself be imprisoned

09:59.150 --> 10:01.150
and willingly die a death by 1,000 cuts?

10:01.150 --> 10:03.610
Knowing full well
that you wouldn't perish,

10:03.630 --> 10:05.090
why did you marry me at all?

10:07.840 --> 10:08.600
Sorry.

10:09.240 --> 10:10.700
I had my own reason to do so.

10:10.870 --> 10:12.270
I just can't tell you why.

10:13.080 --> 10:13.910
Although I learned

10:13.910 --> 10:15.270
the truth afterwards,

10:16.360 --> 10:17.870
I couldn't have done anything

10:17.870 --> 10:19.150
to you since I was a mere

10:19.580 --> 10:22.180
Foundation Establishment Stage cultivator.

10:22.320 --> 10:23.240
Why did you have to

10:23.240 --> 10:24.270
erase my memories?

10:24.270 --> 10:26.600
Why did you continue to
keep me in the dark?

10:30.120 --> 10:31.720
That was never my intention.

10:32.510 --> 10:33.840
Meeting you again in Chongling Valley

10:33.840 --> 10:34.970
was a pure accident.

10:39.440 --> 10:40.120
I know

10:40.840 --> 10:42.570
I've brought you much trouble.

10:42.870 --> 10:44.080
Whatever compensation you want,

10:44.080 --> 10:44.810
just name it.

10:45.630 --> 10:46.360
I'll say yes.

10:48.910 --> 10:51.240
But you just can't give me an explanation,

10:51.670 --> 10:52.240
can you?

11:03.080 --> 11:03.630
Fine.

11:04.850 --> 11:06.910
Then let me ask you one last question.

11:09.510 --> 11:10.080
Ask away.

11:12.270 --> 11:13.800
Where are you at the moment?

11:23.360 --> 11:24.420
Young Sect Master,

11:24.440 --> 11:25.570
what's on your mind?

11:27.120 --> 11:28.250
Something's wrong.

11:29.270 --> 11:30.800
Something is really wrong.

11:31.740 --> 11:32.780
What is wrong?

11:34.480 --> 11:36.810
There's something odd about those people

11:37.120 --> 11:38.250
around Lu Qianqiao.

11:38.840 --> 11:39.600
Could they be

11:39.870 --> 11:40.960
the demonic cultivators

11:40.960 --> 11:42.000
who stole

11:42.000 --> 11:43.660
from the Scripture Pavilion?

11:44.030 --> 11:45.230
What makes you say so?

11:45.550 --> 11:46.630
Previously, when I was talking

11:46.630 --> 11:47.490
to Lu Qianqiao,

11:47.870 --> 11:48.750
those people around him

11:48.750 --> 11:49.950
looked very nervous.

11:50.350 --> 11:51.410
They seemed sneaky

11:51.510 --> 11:52.670
and suspicious.

11:53.150 --> 11:54.120
Chongling Valley

11:54.120 --> 11:55.720
has always been close to mortals.

11:55.720 --> 11:56.720
Could Lu Qianqiao

11:57.030 --> 11:57.720
be covering

11:57.720 --> 11:59.030
for these people?

11:59.840 --> 12:01.120
If that's true,

12:01.720 --> 12:02.870
it'll be bad news.

12:05.030 --> 12:05.550
Why?

12:06.240 --> 12:07.440
Because we can't defeat him.

12:07.440 --> 12:08.640
Are you silly or what?

12:08.970 --> 12:10.630
We don't have to fight those people.

12:10.630 --> 12:11.560
What we need to do

12:11.630 --> 12:13.840
is to figure out their backgrounds first.

12:13.840 --> 12:15.270
If our guess is proven correct,

12:15.270 --> 12:17.000
we'll take them down directly.

12:17.270 --> 12:18.870
There's no need to fear Lu Qianqiao,

12:18.870 --> 12:20.480
since those people stole from us first.

12:20.480 --> 12:21.540
We're in the right.

12:22.150 --> 12:22.680
Let's go!

12:29.550 --> 12:30.840
Young Sect Master Lin.

12:32.630 --> 12:34.200
You seem to be in a hurry.

12:34.600 --> 12:35.960
Where are you heading?

12:37.060 --> 12:38.550
It's none of your business.

12:38.550 --> 12:39.480
Get out of my way.

12:44.160 --> 12:45.100
A bunch of mortals

12:45.100 --> 12:47.240
managed to steal
from your precious library.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.750
The immortal sects in the Central Plains

12:48.750 --> 12:50.880
like yours are really getting better.

12:51.870 --> 12:52.750
Have I been

12:52.750 --> 12:54.630
too polite to you these days?

12:56.200 --> 12:58.030
Catching a bunch of ordinary mortals

12:58.030 --> 12:59.000
actually

12:59.000 --> 13:01.460
requires action
from the young sect master.

13:02.270 --> 13:03.200
Is everyone else

13:03.440 --> 13:05.720
dead here in Lingji Mountain?

13:06.790 --> 13:07.600
Seriously?

13:08.600 --> 13:10.150
Is Jiang Ji also dead?

13:29.240 --> 13:29.750
Lu,

13:30.510 --> 13:31.440
what's with you?

13:32.870 --> 13:34.130
Please say something.

13:45.080 --> 13:46.790
The greatest form is without shape.

13:46.790 --> 13:47.360
Drop!

14:19.390 --> 14:21.790
You caused that incident at Bishui Branch.

14:22.080 --> 14:23.750
After killing Hewabu,

14:24.120 --> 14:25.550
instead of scurrying back

14:25.550 --> 14:26.790
to the Central Plains,

14:26.790 --> 14:29.000
you have the gall to stay in North Xiang.

14:29.670 --> 14:31.130
You must have a death wish.

14:32.030 --> 14:33.760
Did Zuo Yingying tell you that?

14:34.910 --> 14:37.080
She means to set us
fighting against each other

14:37.080 --> 14:39.150
so she can reap the benefits effortlessly.

14:39.150 --> 14:40.000
Too bad

14:40.240 --> 14:41.840
that she won't see it happen.

14:42.000 --> 14:43.200
Because you will soon

14:43.200 --> 14:45.080
be killed by me.

15:00.440 --> 15:01.440
For a burly man,

15:01.910 --> 15:03.510
your moves are quite gentle.

15:03.670 --> 15:05.270
That wasn't a pleasant tune.

15:05.320 --> 15:06.380
Don't you think so?

15:41.480 --> 15:42.410
Cover your ears!

16:06.150 --> 16:06.750
It's over.

16:17.120 --> 16:19.250
You do have a few tricks up your sleeve.

16:22.150 --> 16:22.750
Immortal,

16:23.270 --> 16:24.400
you really found it?

16:25.720 --> 16:27.080
How did you do that?

16:28.960 --> 16:30.910
What are we going to do now?

16:32.550 --> 16:33.080
Sheng.

16:34.240 --> 16:34.720
Sheng!

16:40.750 --> 16:41.610
Senior Sister,

16:41.790 --> 16:42.870
I have to leave first

16:42.870 --> 16:44.070
for an urgent matter.

16:44.270 --> 16:45.730
You should hurry back too.

16:45.790 --> 16:46.720
Try not to delay.

16:47.030 --> 16:47.600
Sheng!

17:11.640 --> 17:13.109
I finally found you.

17:18.960 --> 17:19.920
A sandstorm is coming.

17:19.920 --> 17:20.640
We can't leave the city.

17:20.640 --> 17:22.900
-Where are we going?
-Where are we going?

17:37.000 --> 17:38.310
Who are you looking for?

17:38.310 --> 17:38.720
Run.

17:39.000 --> 17:40.130
Run as far as you can!

18:34.590 --> 18:35.450
Take them away.

18:36.110 --> 18:36.640
Let's go.

18:47.920 --> 18:48.790
I don't care what grudges you have

18:48.790 --> 18:49.920
against each other.

18:50.070 --> 18:51.400
I'll only ask one thing.

18:51.920 --> 18:52.590
Are they

18:52.590 --> 18:55.120
demonic cultivators from Wushuang Society?

18:59.550 --> 19:01.210
I'll take your silence as yes。

19:03.070 --> 19:03.960
Then I'm sorry.

19:04.960 --> 19:05.750
I have to take

19:06.360 --> 19:07.810
these people away today.

19:08.750 --> 19:09.960
Who do you think you are?

19:09.960 --> 19:11.510
You think you can do that
just because you say so?

19:11.510 --> 19:13.750
Since we share the same goal,

19:14.110 --> 19:15.680
why don't we team up?

19:18.960 --> 19:20.640
Dharma King, you're great yourself.

19:20.640 --> 19:22.240
Why join forces with others?

19:22.400 --> 19:24.790
Even I dare not interfere.

19:25.000 --> 19:26.960
Stop making sarcastic remarks.

19:27.310 --> 19:28.480
If they get away,

19:28.720 --> 19:30.850
the Master will hold you accountable.

20:02.960 --> 20:03.830
Who are you?

20:04.030 --> 20:05.510
I am Xia Xuanzi.

20:06.720 --> 20:08.250
What enmity lies between us

20:08.390 --> 20:09.680
that you seek my life?

20:21.960 --> 20:23.420
Do you recognize this man?

20:24.070 --> 20:25.550
I am his father.

20:28.070 --> 20:29.830
I'm going to kill you.

20:30.160 --> 20:32.400
I'm going to kill you!

20:32.750 --> 20:33.830
I did kill him.

20:34.400 --> 20:35.550
If I hadn't,

20:35.720 --> 20:37.180
he would've taken my life.

20:38.240 --> 20:39.700
Glad that you admitted it.

20:39.800 --> 20:42.000
I'll kindly give you a quick death then.

21:38.240 --> 21:39.310
Master, help!

22:05.110 --> 22:06.920
I don't mean to give you a hard time.

22:06.920 --> 22:08.180
But they stole from us,

22:08.550 --> 22:09.110
so I have to

22:09.110 --> 22:10.640
bring them back for a trial.

22:49.200 --> 22:51.400
How dare you, a lapdog for immortal sects,

22:51.400 --> 22:54.000
defile the dignity of the Phoenix God?

22:54.240 --> 22:55.550
You'll be dead meat!

23:07.680 --> 23:09.010
What an evil technique.

23:09.240 --> 23:10.510
What did he just drink?

23:14.530 --> 23:15.430
Spare us, Dharma King!

23:15.430 --> 23:16.760
Please spare our lives!

24:04.240 --> 24:05.170
Anything wrong?

24:06.450 --> 24:07.640
You hold them off for a while.

24:07.640 --> 24:08.070
But...

24:08.480 --> 24:09.340
how do I do that?

24:12.790 --> 24:13.550
Kill them.

24:14.590 --> 24:16.640
Kill all of them!

24:45.790 --> 24:46.480
Mr. Lu.

24:48.930 --> 24:49.860
Leave this to me.

25:07.480 --> 25:08.000
Mr. Lu!

25:08.720 --> 25:09.240
Lu,

25:09.880 --> 25:10.590
wake up!

25:23.110 --> 25:24.170
What are you doing?

25:24.590 --> 25:26.050
He's not the one I am after.

25:26.880 --> 25:28.280
Plus, I know this person.

25:29.350 --> 25:30.410
You can't kill him.

25:34.880 --> 25:35.600
Young Sect Master,

25:35.600 --> 25:37.110
should we keep on fighting?

25:37.110 --> 25:38.770
Do we still want to catch them?

25:38.830 --> 25:39.960
That can wait a bit.

25:52.830 --> 25:54.230
You're at the Void Stage.

25:54.960 --> 25:56.890
The Spirit Projection Technique.

25:58.070 --> 25:59.920
You mere Nascent Soul cultivator,

25:59.920 --> 26:00.980
who really are you?

26:23.640 --> 26:24.700
Why not attack now?

26:24.830 --> 26:25.780
Once he wakes up,

26:26.070 --> 26:27.930
we'll stand no chance of winning!

26:28.030 --> 26:29.160
How will that be?

26:30.000 --> 26:32.550
Dharma King, you haven't used
your full strength yet.

26:32.550 --> 26:34.000
If you do,

26:34.270 --> 26:36.070
none of them can be match for you.

27:07.440 --> 27:08.970
It is truly not easy for you,

27:09.310 --> 27:11.510
a Nascent Soul cultivator, to have caused

27:11.510 --> 27:12.770
this much damage to me.

27:14.440 --> 27:15.400
What a shame

27:16.230 --> 27:17.270
that you're only controlling

27:17.270 --> 27:19.440
a Foundation Establishment Stage
cultivator's body.

27:19.440 --> 27:22.240
Otherwise, things would be
a bit difficult for me.

27:31.640 --> 27:33.500
It's time to put an end to all this!

27:58.550 --> 27:59.640
Impressive.

28:00.440 --> 28:01.310
So are you.

28:03.200 --> 28:04.830
You have
extraordinary cultivation power.

28:04.830 --> 28:07.000
The Foundation Establishment Stage focuses
on physical strength, not the spirit.

28:07.000 --> 28:09.160
The Golden Core Stage focuses
on the spirit, not the heart.

28:09.160 --> 28:11.200
The Nascent Soul Stage focuses
on the heart, not the energy.

28:11.200 --> 28:12.960
Given that, cultivators at these stages

28:12.960 --> 28:15.070
all have easily identified weak spots,

28:15.070 --> 28:18.200
namely their heads and necks, hearts,
and energy bases.

28:18.680 --> 28:20.790
When they reach the Void Stage,

28:21.440 --> 28:23.240
their weak spots become veiled.

28:23.790 --> 28:25.310
I can see that your breathing is steady

28:25.310 --> 28:26.750
and your weaknesses are hidden.

28:26.750 --> 28:27.880
I guess you have reached

28:27.880 --> 28:29.590
the middle phase of the Void Stage.

28:29.590 --> 28:30.720
You know quite a lot.

28:31.240 --> 28:32.040
Not only that,

28:32.310 --> 28:33.200
I'm also aware

28:33.830 --> 28:35.550
that though there is one mere gap
between the middle

28:35.550 --> 28:36.960
and top phases of the Void Stage,

28:36.960 --> 28:39.090
it is utterly challenging to cross it.

28:39.640 --> 28:41.640
The reason is
that towards the end of cultivation,

28:41.640 --> 28:45.240
cultivators usually lack energy,
but have no way to replenish it.

28:45.240 --> 28:47.370
Those who can't overcome this problem

28:48.110 --> 28:49.640
will show their weak spots.

28:56.000 --> 28:57.160
All is over now.

29:03.880 --> 29:05.410
How did you figure that out?

29:09.850 --> 29:12.100
♪ I ask the Nine Heavens:
what is the purpose of this life? ♪

29:12.130 --> 29:14.920
♪ With my spine as my monument,
I shall never kneel ♪

29:15.890 --> 29:17.990
♪ Though this life be wretched,
I will not sink so low ♪

29:18.010 --> 29:20.830
♪ As to become a puppet of fate ♪

29:22.290 --> 29:25.650
♪ Rather than bowing my back
to apologize to the Heavens ♪

29:26.010 --> 29:28.750
♪ I would sooner rewrite
this fated calamity ♪

29:29.140 --> 29:31.660
♪ I demand the story
follow my own desire ♪

29:31.680 --> 29:34.280
♪ To serve as its final conclusion ♪

29:54.590 --> 29:56.720
It's been a pleasure working with you.

30:01.440 --> 30:02.300
Take them down.

30:26.160 --> 30:26.720
Sir,

30:26.740 --> 30:27.850
w-where are you taking me

30:27.850 --> 30:28.480
to?

30:30.350 --> 30:31.350
H-How about this?

30:31.720 --> 30:32.720
Let's make a deal.

30:33.200 --> 30:34.640
I'll leave with my men right away.

30:34.640 --> 30:35.300
And I promise

30:35.300 --> 30:36.000
I'll never mess with

30:36.000 --> 30:36.770
your people again.

30:36.770 --> 30:37.230
Agreed?

30:37.400 --> 30:38.800
P-Please put me down now.

30:40.310 --> 30:41.750
P-Please put me down!

30:53.350 --> 30:54.070
Mr. Lu.

31:19.310 --> 31:20.110
Don't kill me.

31:20.310 --> 31:21.110
Don't kill me!

31:21.510 --> 31:23.160
V-Vajra Xunmu,

31:23.440 --> 31:24.440
I didn't see anything,

31:24.440 --> 31:25.830
and I won't disclose anything.

31:25.830 --> 31:27.030
Please spare my life.

31:27.030 --> 31:27.680
From now on, I...

31:27.680 --> 31:28.920
I will follow you wholeheartedly

31:28.920 --> 31:30.030
and even risk my life for you

31:30.030 --> 31:31.360
with absolute loyalty!

31:31.550 --> 31:32.310
Really?

31:32.750 --> 31:33.270
Really!

31:37.070 --> 31:38.730
Then I'd love to have you prove

31:39.180 --> 31:41.010
your loyalty with your life.

31:59.550 --> 32:02.480
-Greetings, Vajra Xunmu.
-Greetings, Vajra Xunmu.

32:16.440 --> 32:17.570
Greetings, Master.

32:19.590 --> 32:20.480
You're back.

32:20.680 --> 32:21.680
I'm so useless

32:21.790 --> 32:24.050
that I failed to save Dharma King Wenyin.

32:24.310 --> 32:26.030
Who killed him?

32:27.400 --> 32:28.640
The young sect master of Lingji Mountain,

32:28.640 --> 32:29.590
son of Lin An,

32:29.660 --> 32:30.490
Lin Muhan.

32:34.030 --> 32:37.050
[The Crescent Lake]

32:48.110 --> 32:49.040
Wipe your hands.

32:50.440 --> 32:51.440
Thank you, Mr. Lu.

32:58.920 --> 33:01.120
After our parting in Chongling Valley,

33:01.400 --> 33:02.480
I've been having weird dreams

33:02.480 --> 33:03.540
every now and then.

33:04.880 --> 33:06.750
Everything that happens in these dreams

33:06.750 --> 33:08.640
sometimes seems real, and sometimes fake.

33:08.640 --> 33:09.970
It's vague and obscure.

33:11.070 --> 33:13.200
All appears ethereal and disorderly.

33:14.240 --> 33:15.310
But I always feel like I have

33:15.310 --> 33:17.370
experienced everything in reality.

33:20.960 --> 33:22.160
Suppose one's memories

33:22.160 --> 33:23.960
stand for his or her entire life,

33:26.000 --> 33:27.790
then I guess I have died once.

33:32.510 --> 33:34.240
What exactly should I call you?

33:34.920 --> 33:37.110
Are you Lu Huai,
the magistrate of Wei County,

33:37.110 --> 33:39.070
or the Autumn Crimson Blade,
a hero from the martial arts world,

33:39.070 --> 33:39.590
or...

33:39.590 --> 33:40.850
My name is Lu Qianqiao.

33:43.470 --> 33:44.870
"Qian" means thousands,

33:44.960 --> 33:46.560
and "Qiao" means tall trees.

33:46.960 --> 33:48.020
I've told you that.

33:48.680 --> 33:49.790
Yes, you have.

33:50.750 --> 33:52.350
You've said many words to me,

33:53.030 --> 33:54.640
yet not all of them are real.

33:57.480 --> 33:58.940
Should I even believe you?

34:00.640 --> 34:01.500
I did lie to you.

34:02.680 --> 34:04.410
Your anger is understandable.

34:05.160 --> 34:05.680
But right now,

34:05.680 --> 34:07.540
I have a very important task to do.

34:07.830 --> 34:08.960
When I finish it,

34:09.710 --> 34:11.370
I'll give you an explanation.

34:11.710 --> 34:13.510
With that said, please trust me.

34:13.760 --> 34:15.230
I have no intention of harming you.

34:15.230 --> 34:17.110
Aside from erasing my memories,

34:18.030 --> 34:20.090
are you hiding anything else
from me?

34:34.710 --> 34:36.239
Good thing I didn't lose it.

34:37.550 --> 34:38.610
It's a type of candy

34:39.070 --> 34:40.920
made exclusively in North Xiang.

34:40.920 --> 34:41.980
Have you tasted it?

34:43.440 --> 34:44.110
No, never.

34:49.440 --> 34:50.699
Then you can have this.

35:13.480 --> 35:14.410
It's very sweet.

35:19.970 --> 35:21.430
Give me the handkerchief.

35:22.190 --> 35:23.000
I'll wash it.

35:27.800 --> 35:28.630
Lu Qianqiao,

35:29.360 --> 35:31.090
you are a War Demon, aren't you?

35:45.210 --> 35:46.540
What are they doing?

35:46.670 --> 35:47.880
How very baffling.

35:57.800 --> 35:59.130
This is tamarind candy.

35:59.150 --> 36:00.350
It tastes rather sour

36:01.110 --> 36:02.440
without any sweetness.

36:06.590 --> 36:08.320
You don't have a sense of taste,

36:08.630 --> 36:09.150
do you?

36:12.440 --> 36:13.730
You are a War Demon.

36:15.030 --> 36:17.160
I should have thought of that earlier.

36:21.360 --> 36:22.360
You didn't like to eat

36:22.360 --> 36:24.030
when we were in Chongling Valley.

36:24.030 --> 36:25.490
All you took in was liquor.

36:26.800 --> 36:28.590
It's said that War Demons find everything

36:28.590 --> 36:29.920
they eat tastes rotten.

36:30.310 --> 36:31.440
Only the spiciness of liquor

36:31.440 --> 36:32.840
can provide some relief.

36:33.440 --> 36:34.230
Later on, upon hearing

36:34.230 --> 36:35.880
about my erased memories,

36:36.630 --> 36:37.840
I went to Wei County

36:38.670 --> 36:40.270
and visited your residence.

36:40.880 --> 36:41.920
You made all your paintings

36:41.920 --> 36:43.150
with black ink only.

36:43.590 --> 36:44.590
That's because War Demons

36:44.590 --> 36:46.050
cannot tell colors at all.

36:47.190 --> 36:48.630
Suffering the cruel death

36:48.630 --> 36:49.960
by 1,000 cuts

36:51.550 --> 36:53.400
causes severe damage even to a cultivator

36:53.400 --> 36:54.590
at the Void Stage.

36:56.150 --> 36:57.920
Yet it left no scar on you at all.

36:58.710 --> 37:00.440
You healed unbelievably fast.

37:01.280 --> 37:03.810
War Demons are endowed
with that ability too.

37:08.880 --> 37:09.740
Given all that,

37:10.280 --> 37:12.280
you erased my memories to prevent me

37:12.360 --> 37:14.490
from figuring out your real identity.

37:19.590 --> 37:20.800
War Demons

37:21.230 --> 37:22.830
are bloodthirsty by nature.

37:23.840 --> 37:25.440
Many years ago,
to build the heavenly ladder

37:25.440 --> 37:26.920
and ripen the seed of Jianmu Tree,

37:26.920 --> 37:29.510
you War Demons inflicted severe harm
on thousands of innocents.

37:29.510 --> 37:30.360
If it hadn't been for the alliance

37:30.360 --> 37:32.070
of immortal sects and the Youhu Clan,

37:32.070 --> 37:33.200
the world would have

37:33.360 --> 37:35.360
fallen under the rule of War Demons!

37:36.150 --> 37:37.070
It has been

37:38.480 --> 37:40.680
several decades since that brutal war.

37:40.710 --> 37:41.920
Yet the smell of blood

37:42.800 --> 37:44.320
on this land has not faded

37:44.320 --> 37:45.580
after all these years!

37:45.800 --> 37:46.630
The buried bones

37:46.630 --> 37:47.670
of our ancestors in the ground

37:47.670 --> 37:48.930
have not gone cold yet!

37:49.400 --> 37:51.200
There is rage between our races,

37:51.230 --> 37:53.360
and a blood debt of near annihilation!

37:58.230 --> 37:59.030
Then what?

38:00.510 --> 38:01.840
What do you want me to do?

38:03.230 --> 38:05.160
Among the thousands of households

38:05.400 --> 38:07.260
that the War Demons swept through

38:07.440 --> 38:08.700
in hundreds of cities,

38:08.760 --> 38:10.360
not even one in ten survived.

38:11.000 --> 38:12.960
Back then, 24 immortal sects joined forces

38:12.960 --> 38:14.760
to fight against the War Demons.

38:15.000 --> 38:17.000
Half of these sects were destroyed.

38:17.550 --> 38:18.710
At that time, there were

38:18.710 --> 38:20.770
dozens of disciples in Xin Xie Manor.

38:21.110 --> 38:22.970
In the end, I was the only one left.

38:23.840 --> 38:25.170
With such feud in heart,

38:25.510 --> 38:27.110
what do you expect me to do?

38:31.190 --> 38:33.030
Lu Qianqiao, say something!

38:35.400 --> 38:36.800
What do you want me to say?

38:37.550 --> 38:38.880
What do you want me to do?

38:39.500 --> 38:41.230
Do you want me to snap your neck,

38:41.760 --> 38:43.360
devour your flesh and blood,

38:43.500 --> 38:44.900
and torture you to death?

38:45.710 --> 38:47.630
Or do you want me to grovel on the ground

38:47.630 --> 38:48.920
and beg you not to tell anyone

38:48.920 --> 38:49.920
my real identity?

38:53.360 --> 38:54.670
It is true that I tried to conceal

38:54.670 --> 38:55.870
my identity from you.

38:56.230 --> 38:57.830
Because I knew once I said it,

38:58.320 --> 38:59.650
whatever between us...

39:16.880 --> 39:18.340
would have to end this way.

39:23.440 --> 39:24.360
So,

39:25.670 --> 39:27.530
the important task you mentioned

39:28.030 --> 39:29.090
actually refers to

39:29.410 --> 39:31.280
shedding skin, replacing flesh,
renewing bones

39:31.280 --> 39:33.110
and blood, and transforming the heart

39:33.110 --> 39:34.320
in exchange for being reborn

39:34.320 --> 39:36.380
and reincarnating as a human, right?

39:37.320 --> 39:38.980
This approach is known to few.

39:39.760 --> 39:40.150
I happen to

39:40.150 --> 39:42.210
have read about it in an ancient book.

39:43.480 --> 39:44.400
Does it mean

39:45.920 --> 39:47.980
that you're done living as a War Demon

39:48.110 --> 39:49.970
and now craving to become a human?

39:54.920 --> 39:57.250
You War Demons have killed so many people.

39:57.480 --> 39:59.190
Now that you've lost the battle,

39:59.190 --> 40:00.400
you're seeking a new start

40:00.400 --> 40:02.260
by secretly turning into a human?

40:02.280 --> 40:03.940
What right do you have to do so?

40:08.320 --> 40:10.050
I'm just a mediocre cultivator

40:10.800 --> 40:13.060
at the Foundation Establishment Stage.

40:13.070 --> 40:15.270
You might consider me inferior, Mr. Lu,

40:15.510 --> 40:16.840
but I did slay War Demons

40:17.550 --> 40:19.400
with this machete years ago!

40:22.070 --> 40:22.710
Yes.

40:23.280 --> 40:25.810
War Demons have committed
countless crimes.

40:26.440 --> 40:28.070
You're a disciple of an immortal sect.

40:28.070 --> 40:29.800
I am a remnant of the War Demons.

40:30.320 --> 40:31.520
It's only reasonable

40:31.760 --> 40:33.090
that you want to kill me.

40:33.400 --> 40:34.660
But ask yourself this:

40:35.070 --> 40:36.330
have I ever harmed you?

40:36.630 --> 40:37.760
Have I ever hurt you?

40:39.480 --> 40:41.070
All my senior brothers

40:42.000 --> 40:44.360
died at the hands of your kind!

40:45.960 --> 40:48.190
That makes all of you brutal animals!

40:50.920 --> 40:51.880
But I am not.

40:52.440 --> 40:53.640
You are no different.

40:54.030 --> 40:55.440
You are no different!

41:03.360 --> 41:04.000
Fine.

41:05.480 --> 41:06.630
Take my life then.

41:33.140 --> 41:35.190
♪ What do you think is ♪

41:35.240 --> 41:37.590
♪ The most clumsy farewell ♪

41:37.860 --> 41:41.050
♪ The endless slaughter and massacres ♪

41:41.840 --> 41:45.680
♪ Do not wait until that thin snow
on the eaves ♪

41:45.860 --> 41:49.450
♪ Turns a young man's hair white
before you regret it ♪

41:49.470 --> 41:50.820
♪ When do you think ♪

41:50.850 --> 41:53.580
♪ The bloody strife will come to an end? ♪

41:53.600 --> 41:56.940
♪ End these everlasting battles ♪

41:55.710 --> 41:57.070
Do it now.

41:57.560 --> 42:01.490
♪ Holding the morning glow in hand,
I paint the world ♪

41:58.070 --> 41:59.400
Or I'll be leaving then.

42:01.630 --> 42:06.130
♪ Someone's got to clean up this mess ♪
